title: Ice hockey players in Finland 2010/11 - 2017/18
summary: This line chart has an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Number of players, with a total of 8 data points. The chart has 4 significant trends.
The longest trend is extremely positive which exists from 2014/15 to 2010/11.
In a similar manner, the next significant trend is slightly negative which exists from 2017/18 to 2016/17.
On the other hand, the next significant trend is extremely positive which exists from 2016/17 to 2015/16.
In a similar manner, the next significant trend is slightly negative which exists from 2015/16 to 2014/15.
gold: The statistics shows the number of registered ice hockey players in Finland from 2010/11 to 2017/18 . The number of registered ice hockey players in 2017/18 amounted to nearly 73.4 thousand . The highest player number was reported in the previous season ( 2016/17 ) with over 76 thousand players .
